console-setup|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
console-setup: console-setup (Tools for configuring the console using X key maps)
console-setup:
console-setup: This package provides the console with the same keyboard configuration
console-setup: scheme that X Window System has. Besides the keyboard, the package
console-setup: configures also the font on the console.  It includes a rich
console-setup: collection of fonts and supports several languages that would be
console-setup: otherwise unsupported on the console (such as Armenian, Georgian, Lao
console-setup: and Thai).
console-setup:
console-setup: http://packages.debian.org/cs/sid/console-setup
console-setup: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
